HEADWORD: eyeliner
<hw>eye"lin`er</hw> <pr>(⟦imac⟧"l⟦imac⟧`n⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>a cosmetic powder of a dark tint, applied to the eyelid close to
the base of the eyelashes to accentuate the eyes. Compare <contr>eye
shadow</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

